{"tid":211973,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[週六廚房]蒜香蜆意粉","createTime":"2017-04-22T05:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T13:44:13.000Z","uid":30694,"like":81,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04be4a9152e28e37c457c8ff918c2128d072b2d0","tid":211973,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:14:52.000Z","msg":"星期六咁得閒，順便煮下野食滿足下條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n材料：蜆、蒜瓣、辣椒、檸檬，意粉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LNbT6X1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLNbT6X1.jpg&h=909751dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9rk147u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9rk147u.jpg&h=f54a8a94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91da471425bbd16cb4ab12aa9a32817a15c040fb","tid":211973,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:15:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bdf46W7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBdf46W7.jpg&h=9829429e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先去街市買斤蜆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZ98bZM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZ98bZM.jpg&h=937856f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n返到黎拎清水加啲鹽浸，等佢吐晒啲沙出黎，大約1個鐘就夠"},{"pid":"fac7a80c6658a8011cc1699a245b9250d9c615cf","tid":211973,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/741i7d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F741i7d5.jpg&h=befd1b33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將蒜，辣椒切碎，食得辣就切多幾條辣椒，唔得就一條都好夠味，隨意<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qCZN64j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqCZN64j.jpg&h=27f044d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j352294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj352294.jpg&h=a278aa49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲蜆浸夠1個鐘，再拎啲清水洗下佢，咁就冇晒啲沙"},{"pid":"86a56bc6b240a113c00551afb6bf366853be5a19","tid":211973,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:17:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39e76222ed37144e15860a8e84999cf74ae7aba0","tid":211973,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K3DE6c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK3DE6c0.jpg&h=f038dc64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住煲水煮意粉，水滾之後記得落鹽，之後再落意粉，煮8分鐘，每隻意粉都唔同，跟個包裝話煮幾耐再減1分鐘就可以<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GbpFig7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGbpFig7.jpg&h=9f2a4d17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開中火爆紅隻鑊，再落油<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wei75W2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwei75W2.jpg&h=226bfdd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倒晒啲蜆落去炒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68BD48j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68BD48j.jpg&h=54c33a61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兜兩野，啲蜆兩分鐘到就會開"},{"pid":"a3a5a8c32e273e1dff240d2be3afdc0b82d21cd0","tid":211973,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p6jg2e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp6jg2e7.jpg&h=563dfe37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後落蒜頭，辣椒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQ16306.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQ16306.jpg&h=faef39d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再兜下佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JEKWf19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJEKWf19.jpg&h=09d788a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上次煮野淨左枝白酒，倒埋落去，唔加都得，只係會香啲"},{"pid":"5b395e6d019420ee9b363fdfbadc630e4e0d70f5","tid":211973,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C0rZ3D6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC0rZ3D6.jpg&h=7e6720dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n刨啲檸檬皮落去，再兜兩野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6O1EoS8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6O1EoS8.jpg&h=89df5a04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個時候啲意粉已經煮好，倒埋落去啲蜆到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C5r19Pe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC5r19Pe.jpg&h=2d1af522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後係咁兜，啲意粉就會索啲蜆汁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iva9xii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiva9xii.jpg&h=570e7b15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n煮好之前我加左啲牛油，可以令意粉睇落更有光澤，一樣係可以唔加，隨意<br />\n手震對焦唔到，Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15037a0863dc33838a5ca52edad31d1951399e8a","tid":211973,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:23:39.000Z","msg":"最尾又兜下佢，就可以上碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n煮好左條女就即刻拎左出去食，我都未影得切相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得返啲殼就唔影喇，下次有機會煮再影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fed166211ba0fb369504aada11032f8acba348","tid":211973,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:24:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蜆幾錢斤？</blockquote><br />\n我個邊個街市24蚊斤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddcdc99c158fcd27605118b73ac4ec08b13218d","tid":211973,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:24:33.000Z","msg":"整黎溝女真心唔錯，諗下下星期有咩野好煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab43db8fd71e4a39d8236751e4e427f808480095","tid":211973,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:37:57.000Z","msg":"有樣野唔記得講，記得拎走啲死既蜆，即係唔開蓋既，如果唔係會臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ad0e3deb8a95fe179f3e60c96600c549415ac0","tid":211973,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:38:10.000Z","msg":"好有心機<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387455792be08752674ead068ab8aa79a8269555","tid":211973,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:39:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蜆幾錢斤？</blockquote><br />\n我個邊個街市24蚊斤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常都要加一蚊兩蚊，因為好難啱啱好夠一斤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9808e312e8e50253d892d60c29bd8117d0111a71","tid":211973,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好有心機<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1885e92ff0f3aebd0a1bb673600dd25ad69a8a","tid":211973,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:39:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有樣野唔記得講，記得拎走啲死既蜆，即係唔開蓋既，如果唔係會臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買嗰陣聽聲"},{"pid":"c9a1ea8e306115f88576ad176747ee7596e7eedb","tid":211973,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:41:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有樣野唔記得講，記得拎走啲死既蜆，即係唔開蓋既，如果唔係會臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買嗰陣聽聲</blockquote><br />\n聽咩聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedc3f2029b3309fe09ef94ff150e7633f7c8e31","tid":211973,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有樣野唔記得講，記得拎走啲死既蜆，即係唔開蓋既，如果唔係會臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係炒個陣"},{"pid":"4c88e4a1572f53eb4197774d0a1fc7e483792328","tid":211973,"uid":33908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:42:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有樣野唔記得講，記得拎走啲死既蜆，即係唔開蓋既，如果唔係會臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買嗰陣聽聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n逐隻敲俾啊姐屌到飛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24155f630eefad786a15587e7cf4d7d4f9c37354","tid":211973,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:44:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有樣野唔記得講，記得拎走啲死既蜆，即係唔開蓋既，如果唔係會臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買嗰陣聽聲</blockquote><br />\n聽咩聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我老婆屋企以前做海鮮<br />\n佢用shaw kai<br />\n有bass 就死嘅<br />\nExperience"},{"pid":"847ca2e3a02172b30c69e0c96c13c533f488e23c","tid":211973,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:47:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有樣野唔記得講，記得拎走啲死既蜆，即係唔開蓋既，如果唔係會臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買嗰陣聽聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n逐隻敲俾啊姐屌到飛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以後唔撚賣海鮮比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11cbd0ab22610a65165900cae821a35ec68cd20","tid":211973,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有樣野唔記得講，記得拎走啲死既蜆，即係唔開蓋既，如果唔係會臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買嗰陣聽聲</blockquote><br />\n聽咩聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我老婆屋企以前做海鮮<br />\n佢用shaw kai<br />\n有bass 就死嘅<br />\nExperience</blockquote><br />\n學到野<img src=\"/a